rows.label: kizunainn060_msg0002
rows.name:
It seems one can worship a splendid
scenery unlike anything seen before
from the exit of the Norem Cloudway.

rows.label: kizunainn060_msg0003
rows.name:
Perhaps, it will be a place
befitting of Me.

rows.label: kizunainn060_msg0004
rows.name:
I permit you bastards to guide me
to the Norem Cloudway.
Prepare immediately!
